## migrations
- schema migrations are embedded in the Rust binary and run inside transactions when a Store is opened @implemented
- label: applied migrations are recorded with version, name, checksum, and applied_at, and checksum mismatches stop the command with an actionable error
  command: bash tests/facts/store_schema_migrations.sh migration_checksum_mismatch
  tags: [implemented]

