  command: bash tests/facts/cli_hooks.sh hook_failure_or_timeout_reports_committed_mutation
  tags: [implemented]
- label: Hook stdout and stderr capture are capped at 8192 bytes each and the cap values are documented in command help
  command: bash tests/facts/cli_hooks.sh hook_output_capture_caps_and_help
  tags: [implemented]
- label: link and unlink Hooks evaluate their Query against the source Record and receive AGENT_STORE_REL matching the Link relation
